data.oai_dc:dc: This data includes height (cm) measures of 104 female Asian elephants aged 20-50, along with their censorship status (1=dead, 0=alive), and their age at censorship or death. This also includes their reproductive status, their birth origin (1=wild caught, 0=captive born), and their age at capture if they are wild caught (captive born age at capture= 0).
